<CSSBorder-inline-start-style>
<summary>
The <strong><c>border-inline-start-style</c></strong> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</see> property defines the style of the logical inline start border of an element, which maps to a physical border style depending on the element's writing mode, directionality, and text orientation. It corresponds to the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-style">border-top-style</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-style">border-right-style</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-style">border-bottom-style</see>, or <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-style">border-left-style</see> property depending on the values defined for <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode">writing-mode</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction">direction</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-orientation">text-orientation</see>.
</summary>
<remarks>
<para>EmbedInteractiveExample("pages/css/border-inline-start-style.html")</para>
<para>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_logical_properties_and_values">CSS Logical Properties and Values</see><br/>-This property maps to one of the physical border properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-style">border-top-style</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-style">border-right-style</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-style">border-bottom-style</see>, or <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-style">border-left-style</see>.<br/>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/writing-mode">writing-mode</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/direction">direction</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/text-orientation">text-orientation</see><br/></para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-inline-start-style"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
</CSSBorder-inline-start-style>
